profile:
Conworx Group has been at the forefront of the construction and strata maintenance industry. Conworx rapidly gained a reputation for excellence thanks to the professionalism and know-how of its highly specialized team of experts.
 
This powerful team enables the company to expand its reach and offer its services across the Lower Mainland. 
 
Conworx is also known as a provider of a wide range of construction-related solutions. These play a key role in all aspects pertaining to safety, quality, and efficiency.
